OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FOur roads are a 'national disgrace',
OL,8,Fthat's according to a report that says
OL,9,Fthe cost of bringing roads in England
OL,10,Fand Wales up to scratch is #18.6
OL,11,Fbillion, as Philip Sime reports.
OL,13,FThe estimated cost of bringing pothole-
OL,14,Fplagued local roads in England and
OL,15,FWales up to scratch has risen to a
OL,16,Frecord #18.6 billion, according to a
OL,17,Fnew report, which branded the
OL,18,Fsituation "a national disgrace".
OL,26,@zD@KOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
