OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773876312
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FResearch by the Asphalt Industry
OL,8,FAlliance (AIA) found only 51% of the
OL,9,Flocal road network is reported to be
OL,10,Fin good condition.
OL,12,FIt claimed this shows extra investment
OL,13,Fto tackle potholes has failed to
OL,14,Fdeliver "noticeable improvements".
OL,16,FRoads are only being resurfaced, on
OL,17,Faverage, once every 97 years.
OL,19,FA total of 1.9 million potholes were
OL,20,Ffilled over the last year.
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773876312
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FDavid Giles, who chairs the AIA, said
OL,8,Fnoticeable improvements "lie a long
OL,9,Fway off".
OL,11,FHe said: "I think all road users would
OL,12,Fagree that the condition of our local
OL,13,Froads has become a national disgrace."
OL,15,FTotal local road maintenance funding
OL,16,Ffor England provided by the government
OL,17,Fin the 2025/26 financial year was
OL,18,Fnearly #1.6 billion, representing a
OL,19,F#500 million uplift compared with the
OL,20,Fprevious 12 months.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@HO]sD@JOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773876312
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FA total of #7.3 billion has been
OL,8,Fannounced for the four years up to the
OL,9,F2029/30 financial year.
OL,11,FMr Giles said: "While local authority
OL,12,Fhighway engineers told us they are
OL,13,Fcautiously optimistic that the
OL,14,Fincreased funding will help them stem
OL,15,Ffurther decline, it is not the silver
OL,16,Fbullet that will clear the backlog of
OL,17,Frepairs any time soon.
OL,26,@sD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773876312
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,F"It will be some time before the
OL,8,Fimpact of increased funding levels, if
OL,9,Ffully delivered, will be noticed by
OL,10,Fthe public."
OL,12,FHe added that "the dial could be moved
OL,13,Fquicker" if the government's
OL,14,Fcommitment to additional funding was
OL,15,Ffront-loaded rather than "ramping up
OL,16,Fin the years to 2030".
OL,18,FThe AIA's annual Alarm (annual local
OL,19,Fauthority road maintenance) report is
OL,20,Fbased on a survey of local authorities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@LO]tD@OOUuD@HO]wD@ZOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
