CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773876312
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FIt found bringing local roads up to
OL,8,Fideal conditions would cost #18.6
OL,9,Fbillion and take 12 years to complete.
OL,11,FHighway maintenance budgets for the
OL,12,F2025/26 financial year are reported to
OL,13,Fhave increased by 17% compared with
OL,14,Fthe previous 12 months, to an average
OL,15,Fof #30.5 million per authority.
OL,17,FMore than half of that (54%) is being
OL,18,Fspent on the surface and structure of
OL,19,Froads.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
