OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FPotholes are often formed when
OL,8,Frainfall enters cracks in the road
OL,9,Fand, when the temperature drops below
OL,10,F0C , freezes and expands, creating
OL,11,Fbigger cracks.
OL,13,FAA president Edmund King warned that
OL,14,F"much more needs to be done to
OL,15,Feradicate this plague of potholes".
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
