OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FHe added: "We have been seeing with
OL,8,Four own eyes, and feeling with our
OL,9,Fwheels, how record wet weather linked
OL,10,Fto substandard roads has led to many
OL,11,Flocal roads becoming patchwork
OL,12,Fobstacle courses."
OL,14,FTom Hunt, who chairs the Local
OL,15,FGovernment Association's inclusive
OL,16,Fgrowth committee, said the increase in
OL,17,Ffunding for fixing roads is "positive"
OL,18,Fbut "more action is needed for
OL,19,Fcouncils to bring roads up to scratch".
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@RO]yD@]OUyD@fO]zD@EOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
