OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FColin Brown, director of campaigns and
OL,8,Fpolitical engagement at lobbying
OL,9,Forganisation Motorcycle Action Group,
OL,10,Fcited government figures showing road
OL,11,Fsurface conditions contribute to twice
OL,12,Fthe proportion of killed or seriously
OL,13,Finjured motorcyclists compared with
OL,14,Fcar occupants and cyclists.
OL,16,FHe said: "Riders aren't complaining
OL,17,Fabout cracked roads because of the
OL,18,Fdamage to their tyres ` it's the added
OL,19,Frisk of dying on them."
OL,26,@xD@JOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
