OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FA Department for Transport
OL,8,Fspokesperson said the report "rightly
OL,9,Fhighlights the need to improve our
OL,10,Froads" and the government has raised
OL,11,Fthe funding level to help councils
OL,12,F"fix the pothole plague".
OL,14,FHe added: "We're already seeing
OL,15,Fprogress, with 15% more
OL,16,Fpotholeprevention works carried out
OL,17,Fin 2025 compared to 2024 and reversing
OL,18,Fa nearly decade-long decline in road
OL,19,Frepair works."
